metadata.name: POOTY TANG- JAYPROB & ROCKY SNYDA
metadata.description: JAYPROB and Rocky Snyda dive into their acting bag to give a modern take on the cult classic “Pooty Tang”. When JAYPROB and Rocky Snyda join forces they are FUTRxLGND, recording artists and residents of “BRONXLYN” who have now sold 4 NFTS since entering web 3 in January 2022.
